t = int(input())
while t > 0:
    (a1, a2, a3, c1, c2, c3) = list(map(int, input().split()))
    l = [a1, a2, a3]
    l.sort()
    l1 = [c1, c2, c3]
    l1.sort()
    if l.index(a1) == l1.index(c1) and l.index(a2) == l1.index(c2) and (l.index(a3) == l1.index(c3)):
        print('FAIR')
    else:
        print('NOT FAIR')
    t -= 1
